OL,3,CEx-Post Office clerk recalls arrest in
OL,4,Cfront of children and years of shame
OL,6,FA victim of the flawed Horizon
OL,7,Faccounting system, the 42-year-old
OL,8,Fspoke out after finally being cleared
OL,9,Fon Tuesday (13 February).
OL,11,F"I tried and I tried and I couldn't
OL,12,Ffind the #1,000 anywhere," Ms Falcon
OL,13,Ftold the PA news agency.
OL,15,FShe wondered if she had mistyped a
OL,16,Ftransaction, mistakenly recording a
OL,17,F#10 deposit as a #1,000.
