OL,6,F"Then I thought, had someone grabbed
OL,7,Fcash through the parcel hatch? I
OL,8,Fthought of every scenario possible,"
OL,9,Fshe added.
OL,11,F"It drove me mad, I went nuts thinking
OL,12,Fabout it."
OL,14,FWhat she did not know at the time was
OL,15,Fthat the Horizon system, which could
OL,16,Fbe accessed remotely, could throw out
OL,17,Faccounting errors.
