OL,6,F"Things were always going wrong with
OL,7,Fthe system," she said. "I was on the
OL,8,Fphone all the time and we had
OL,9,Fengineers out all the time.
OL,11,F"In the end, we didn't bother ringing
OL,12,Fthem, we just rebooted the system
OL,13,Fourselves if the problem was
OL,14,Fpersistent."
