OL,3,CEx-Post Office clerk recalls arrest in
OL,4,Cfront of children and years of shame
OL,6,FMs Falcon, a mother-of-four at the
OL,7,Ftime and who was pregnant with her
OL,8,Ffifth child when she was sentenced,
OL,9,Fwas terrified to bring up the missing
OL,10,F#1,000 with the Postmistress as she
OL,11,Fwas afraid she would have to make up
OL,12,Fthe cash herself.
OL,14,FRemembering the hearing where she
OL,15,Fadmitted fraud on the instruction of
OL,16,Fher barrister, Ms Falcon said: "The
OL,17,Fjudge made me feel really stupid in
OL,18,Fcourt, saying if I hadn't stolen
OL,19,Fanything why was I trying to pay the
OL,20,Fmoney back?
