OL,3,CEx-Post Office clerk recalls arrest in
OL,4,Cfront of children and years of shame
OL,6,F"But I hadn't stolen it, the money had
OL,7,Fjust vanished."
OL,9,FMs Falcon, who is a Royalist, said:
OL,10,F"When it got to court, it was the
OL,11,FQueen versus Jacqueline Falcon.
OL,13,F"How on earth can I beat that one, on
OL,14,Fmy word, just because I had been a
OL,15,Fgood citizen? So you just accept it."
OL,17,FShe had support from neighbours and
OL,18,Ffamily, but not, she said, from
OL,19,Feveryone in the small community where
OL,20,Fshe still lives.
