OL,3,CEx-Post Office clerk recalls arrest in
OL,4,Cfront of children and years of shame
OL,6,F"A lot of my customers stuck by me and
OL,7,Fdidn't believe I had done anything
OL,8,Fwrong, and a lot of those older ones
OL,9,Fhave now passed away," continued Ms
OL,10,FFalcon.
OL,12,F"Some people have been really nasty to
OL,13,Fme. My oldest two were 15 and 13 at
OL,14,Fthe time and were bullied at school.
OL,16,F"One person said 'your mum only got
OL,17,Fpregnant to avoid going to prison'."
