OL,3,CEx-Post Office clerk recalls arrest in
OL,4,Cfront of children and years of shame
OL,6,FMs Falcon was handed a three-month
OL,7,Fjail sentence, suspended for 12 months
OL,8,Fand ordered to pay #933.69, which was
OL,9,Foutstanding from the missing #1,000
OL,10,Fwhen she was sentenced at Newcastle
OL,11,FCrown Court in 2015.
OL,13,FShe said she became almost reclusive,
OL,14,Fnot wanting to leave the house in case
OL,15,Fsomeone made a nasty remark or a dirty
OL,16,Flook.
OL,18,FMs Falcon hated to think about the
OL,19,FPost Office and did not follow the
OL,20,FHorizon scandal.
