OL,3,CEx-Post Office clerk recalls arrest in
OL,4,Cfront of children and years of shame
OL,6,FThen, out of the blue, a letter from
OL,7,Fthe Criminal Cases Review Commission,
OL,8,Fwhich investigates miscarriages of
OL,9,Fjustice, landed on her doormat,
OL,10,Finforming her she could have a case
OL,11,Ffor appeal.
OL,13,FMs Falcon was prosecuted by the Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service, not the Post
OL,15,FOffice like many postmasters, and the
OL,16,FCPS indicated it would not have
OL,17,Fbrought the case against her had it
OL,18,Fknown about Horizon's major flaws, as
OL,19,Fit would not have been in the public
OL,20,Finterest.
