OL,6,FShe also felt it was better to have
OL,7,Fhad her day in court ` or at least
OL,8,Ffollowing the events via a video link
OL,9,Ffrom home ` and not to be part of a
OL,10,F"mass-exoneration process".
OL,12,FShe said: "I am much happier it is
OL,13,Fdone properly, a judge has looked at
OL,14,Fit, solicitors have looked at it. It
OL,15,Fshould be done right."
OL,17,FMs Falcon praised the ITV drama Mr
OL,18,FBates vs The Post Office, saying: "I
OL,19,Fthought it was brilliant.
