OL,3,CEx-Post Office clerk recalls arrest in
OL,4,Cfront of children and years of shame
OL,6,F"It brought back memories which were
OL,7,Fhorrendous, things I had not thought
OL,8,Fabout in years, things I had tried to
OL,9,Fget out of my memory.
OL,11,F"People will be more understanding now
OL,12,Fand the show did a good job of
OL,13,Fexplaining the problem ` it was a
OL,14,Fcomplicated system."
OL,16,FDespite her ordeal, she recognised
OL,17,Fother victims have had it worse.
