OL,6,FShe said: "Some people have lost their
OL,7,Fhome, their business or committed
OL,8,Fsuicide. I'm pleased it was 'just'
OL,9,F#1,000 as some people ended up being
OL,10,Fcharged for stealing #40-#50,000.
OL,12,F"I would have gone to prison if it had
OL,13,Fbeen that much."
OL,15,FThe Crown Prosecution Service did not
OL,16,Foppose her appeal,
